{
  "prompt": "A modern, clean, and minimalist redesign of a SCADA (Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition) interface. The interface should focus on three large vertical tanks aligned on the left side of the screen. Each tank has a small output line represented by a colored pipe (e.g., red, blue, purple). These output lines flow horizontally toward the right side, where they cleanly split and connect to smaller labeled tanks or input modules. The layout avoids visual clutter, using clear flow arrows, clean typography, and color-coded paths to show system logic without overlapping pipes or chaotic structure. The background is neutral or dark, and all elements are organized with intentional spacing, like a symbolic diagram rather than a noisy machine schematic. Inspired by modern UX principles and recursion-based system layout.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A simplified 2D digital SCADA (Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition) system interface. On the left side, three large tanks (with no internal color) each have a short output pipe segment labeled with a unique color (red, blue, green). These short segments stop before reaching the center. On the right side of the image is a single rectangular processing/output unit with three short input pipe segments matching the tank colors (red, blue, green) but not physically connected to the tanks ‚Äî suggesting abstract or wireless connection. The overall layout is clean and minimalist, with a dark or neutral background, minimal color usage beyond the three lines, and no clutter or excessive gauges. The focus is on visual clarity and symbolic signal mapping without full pipe routing.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A minimal, futuristic SCADA (Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition) interface concept designed with clarity and symbolic logic. The interface contains three tanks labeled Red, Blue, and Green at the top. Each tank has a short color segment beneath it (not full pipes), representing an output connection. On the right side, there's an Output unit showing matching short red, blue, and green segments to indicate where the lines terminate. In the middle-bottom section, there is a clean row of interface icons, modular in style, with simple shapes that allow interaction or control. The entire layout avoids pipe clutter, uses color coding minimally, and focuses on symbolic connectivity. The display is sharp, clean, and optimized for filtering by color combinations ‚Äî allowing the user to display only red, only blue, only green, or intersections like red + green, with irrelevant paths hidden.",
  "size": "1024x768"
}

{
  "prompt": "A technical conceptual diagram of a three-tiered mobile mesh network architecture called EchoNet. Tier 1 shows phones connected in a local mesh network using short-range technologies like Wi-Fi Direct and Bluetooth. Tier 2 shows cellular towers acting as relay nodes with minimal logic, connecting when local mesh fails. Tier 3 shows an AI system optimizing connections and predicting routes. The image includes arrows indicating communication paths, device icons, towers, and AI cloud overlays. Clean digital style, with labeled layers and color-coded tiers for clarity.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic, elegantly designed female android inspired by Ava from Ex Machina. She has an hourglass figure with balanced proportions: approximately 5'7\" tall, bust 36-38 inches, waist 24-25 inches, hips 36-38 inches. Her synthetic skin is semi-translucent with a soft inner glow, revealing hints of inner circuitry beneath. Her face is symmetrical and expressive with large, violet-silver eyes, a precise jawline, and a calm, intelligent expression. Her hair is silky platinum blonde, shoulder-length, and slightly shimmering. She has subtle glowing tattoos under the skin on her arms and shoulders. Her body surface shifts in texture: soft and warm in human-contact areas, with visible high-tech components on the limbs and torso. She stands in a soft ambient environment resembling a sci-fi lab or peaceful high-tech sanctuary.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A hyper-realistic digital rendering of a feminine humanoid robot with a minimalist, elegant design. She has a slim and athletic build with subtle curves, small bust (A to B cup), and proportionally balanced hips that are not overly wide. Her facial features are inspired by Japanese aesthetics‚Äîrefined, symmetrical, soft, and emotionally expressive. The skin has a smooth, light synthetic sheen, with visible but sleek panel lines suggesting advanced cybernetic structure. Her eyes are large and thoughtful, with a gentle glow. She stands in a soft-lit futuristic environment, evoking both strength and serenity.",
